    "total_tags": 330,
    "v1_to_v1.1_change": "Session 13 second pass: split monolithic 'verdict' dimension into 4 sub-dimensions (quality / difficulty / length / recommendation) for cleaner orthogonality. No tags renamed or removed, just regrouped."
